00:34:49.150 --> 00:34:52.810
interpretation. So I was amazed with the

611
00:34:52.850 --> 00:34:56.850
proportion of what we thought to be benign that

612
00:34:56.890 --> 00:35:00.349
is probably not benign, and we're reporting them as benign,

613
00:35:01.310 --> 00:35:05.090
whereas we shouldn't. 23, 25% of them could

