00:35:13.350 --> 00:35:14.830
Right. Which is a very different thing, right?

619
00:35:14.870 --> 00:35:16.470
But they are not called at all, right?

620
00:35:16.610 --> 00:35:16.950
So we-

621
00:35:17.290 --> 00:35:19.040
That's true. You're not doing anything with them genetically.

