00:35:19.090 --> 00:35:20.990
Typically, we don't really report them, so-

623
00:35:21.150 --> 00:35:21.220
Right

624
00:35:21.370 --> 00:35:22.770
... this is disturbing.

625
00:35:22.950 --> 00:35:26.880
Yes. And so in countries and companies

626
00:35:26.890 --> 00:35:28.750
that have not reported out the VUS,

627
00:35:29.930 --> 00:35:33.830
it raises a question of how many variants have they left behind and missed

628
00:35:34.610 --> 00:35:36.170
because they didn't report the information.

629
00:35:36.250 --> 00:35:39.690
Absolutely. But the clinicians don't want them in the report.

630
00:35:39.730 --> 00:35:41.350
They say, "No," they get-

631
00:35:41.770 --> 00:35:42.750
They don't want them because-

632
00:35:42.760 --> 00:35:43.489
... confuse the patient.

633
00:35:43.590 --> 00:35:46.260
Well, in fairness to the clinicians, they didn't want them because they didn't know

634
00:35:46.290 --> 00:35:46.890
what to do with them.

635
00:35:46.920 --> 00:35:46.920
Exactly.

636
00:35:46.930 --> 00:35:48.190
They couldn't do anything with them.

637
00:35:48.350 --> 00:35:48.530
Exactly.

638
00:35:48.650 --> 00:35:51.770
Now with these large MAVE studies, I think we're getting to the point.

