00:35:51.850 --> 00:35:55.310
I'm not saying we're there today, but we're very close to being able

640
00:35:55.390 --> 00:35:59.090
to say a lot about most of these variants.

641
00:35:59.170 --> 00:36:00.590
Amazing. Very good work.

