00:36:45.966 --> 00:36:49.686
So how do we evaluate this ClinVar versus MAVE versus

656
00:36:50.146 --> 00:36:51.526
whatever reports tell us?

657
00:36:52.306 --> 00:36:52.426
Well,

658
00:36:54.186 --> 00:36:57.406
what we do with most of this genetic information is just predict risks.

