00:38:53.146 --> 00:38:57.066
might inform the phenotypes a little bit and tell us what's real and what's not

697
00:38:57.086 --> 00:38:57.386
real.

698
00:38:59.426 --> 00:39:03.146
It could be that in one cell type, a mutation's

